reviewText: I thought it would only be of You Tube quality; it was very good.  It 'was worth the money and the seller did a good job.  Thanks!

Instructions for a simple field strip can be found in the owner's manual.  However, for a complete disassembly this video is a must have.  There are some intricacies with this weapon that are covered in great detail that will help the owner avoid a costly mistake.  This video is professionally made with detailed closeups of all the steps needed to completely disassemble the firearm and comes highly recommended.
